application_details.scheme_name: Silverdale Industrial Estate Silverdale Road Hayes

description: Demolition of existing buildings and redevelopment of the site to provide a podium at ground level and buildings ranging from four storeys to nine storeys, comprising 122 residential units (Use Class C3) and 230 sq.m of flexible commercial space (Use Classes A1, A3, B1, D1 or D2), together with associated car parking, vehicular access, landscaping, infrastructure works and the extension of Shackles Dock.
